title: Order Saga - Distributed Transaction

participant API Gateway as GW
participant Order Service as Orders
participant Payment Service as Pay
participant Inventory Service as Inv
participant Shipping Service as Ship
participant Notification Service as Notify

GW->>Orders: POST /orders { items, payment }
Orders->>Orders: Create order (PENDING)
Orders->>Inv: Reserve inventory
Inv-->>Orders: Inventory reserved
Orders->>Pay: Charge payment
Pay->>Pay: Process credit card
Pay-->>Orders: Payment confirmed (txnId)
note over Orders: Update status=CONFIRMED
Orders->>Ship: Schedule shipment
Ship-->>Orders: Shipment scheduled (trackingId)
Orders->>Notify: Send confirmation email
Notify-->>Orders: Email queued
Orders-->>GW: 201 Created { orderId, trackingId }
note over Orders, Pay: On failure: compensating transactions
